<A>__{danny walking home. sparse traffic on the street. he walks with his head down and his hands thrust in his pockets. a red car approaches from the opposite direction. it slows as it passes danny. danny looks over. the driver is obscured by the reflected glare of a streetlight, but it is obvious that he is staring right at danny. danny plays it cool. keeps walking. the red car pulls a slow u turn. danny hauls ass. the red car catching up.}
